headlines.description: The United States came from behind in impressive fashion to beat Costa Rica in its CONCACAF World Cup qualifier at the new home of Columbus Crew.

video.headline: Sergino Dest rockets in goal for USMNT to level score

headlines.description: Hector Moreno and Raul Jimenez scored at the Estadio Cuscatlan as Mexico beat El Salvador 2-0 on Wednesday in World Cup qualifying.
headlines.shortLinkText: Moreno, Jimenez see Mexico past El Salvador
